

* Description							   :sys:anal:

* Usage

> iostat

+ Display cpu statistics*

> iostat -c

+ Display i/o statistics*

> iostat -d

+ Display network statistics*

> iostat -n

+ Display statistics for a device*

> iostat -p <device>

+ Display timestamp information*

> iostat -t

+ Display extended information*

> iostat -x

> iostat -x <device>

+ Execute every x seconds*

> iostat x

end this with CTRL-C

> iostat x y

this will perform iostat every x second y times

+ Display LVM information*

> iostat -N

+ adding -m to any of these will produce the output in mb/s
